n><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A user-defined simplification procedure used by the `cbv` tactic.\nThe body must have type `Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Simproc` (`Expr → SimpM Result`).\nProcedures are indexed by a discrimination tree pattern and fire at one of three phases:\n`↓` (pre), `cbv_eval` (eval), or `↑` (post, default).\n","docLink":"./Init/CbvSimproc.html#Lean.Parser.«command__Cbv_simproc____(_):=_»","kind":"def","line":19,"name":"Lean.Parser.«command__Cbv_simproc____(_):=_»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Init/CbvSimproc.lean#L19-L25"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/CbvSimproc.html#Lean.Parser.cbvSimprocEval\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">cbvSimprocEval</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/CbvSimproc.html#Lean.Parser.cbvSimprocEval","kind":"def","line":17,"name":"Lean.Parser.cbvSimprocEval","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Init/CbvSimproc.lean#L17-L17"}}],"imports":["Init.Data.ToString.Name","Init.Meta.Defs","Init.Tactics"],"instances":[],"name":"Init.CbvSimproc"}